            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The specific writing of the beta is frequent throughout the Moutoullas monument but also in other churches in Cyprus of the end of the 13th century such as the church of the Transfiguration of the Saviour in Sotera Ammochostou. Probably the painter came from the same workshop.</p>
